<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      border: 0;
      font-size: 100%;
    }

    .container {
      width: 100%;
      height: 400px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 32px 0px;
    }

    .content {
      width: 80%;
      height: 100%;
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 16px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, .1);
      padding: 12px;
    }

    .header {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 26px;
      line-height: 28px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #7fc128;
    }

    .title {
      margin: 30px 0px 12px 0px;
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .code {
      margin: 36px 0px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .code-txt {
      background-color: #7fc128;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      color: aliceblue;
      font-size: 24px;
      line-height: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="content">
      <p class="header">Houston Service</p>
      <p class="title">Hi,</p>
      <div class="text">
        Please use the verification code below on the Houston website:
      </div>
      <div class="code">
        <span class="code-txt">{{data.code}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="text">
        If you didn't request this, you can ignore this email or let us know.
        </br>
        Thanks !
        </br>
        Develop Team
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>